TO INTRODUCE YOU.

699
00:42:48,833 --> 00:42:52,068
OH, MY GOD.
YEAH, IF YOU COULD INTRODUCE ME,
THAT WOULD BE AMAZING.

700
00:42:52,070 --> 00:42:54,137
WELL, I MEAN, MAYBE.
I DON'T KNOW.

701
00:42:54,139 --> 00:42:56,139
