997
00:55:15,746 --> 00:55:18,547
I DON'T MIND.
YEAH.
COLIN, WE'RE FLATTERED.

998
00:55:18,549 --> 00:55:21,383
YEAH, WELL, UH, J.R. DIDN'T KNOW
HOW TO READ UNTIL SHE WAS TEN.

999
00:55:21,385 --> 00:55:23,719
ISN'T THAT HILARIOUS?
