1004
00:55:33,798 --> 00:55:35,798
EXCUSE ME.

1005
00:55:35,800 --> 00:55:37,333
HI.

1006
00:55:37,335 --> 00:55:40,569
I'M COLIN.

1007
00:55:40,571 --> 00:55:42,071
YOU KNOW,
IT'S JUST HARD,

1008
00:55:42,073 --> 00:55:43,939
