00:55:47,845 --> 00:55:50,846
OH, YOU GOT MARRIED
AND HAD A KID ALREADY?

1011
00:55:50,848 --> 00:55:52,648
WELL, OF COURSE I DID.

1012
00:55:52,650 --> 00:55:55,117
