TO ME.

1028
00:56:29,653 --> 00:56:32,554
IS THAT THE WORD
I'M LOOKING FOR?
IT IS.

1029
00:56:32,556 --> 00:56:34,723
SO YOU CHOOSE
TO EXPRESS YOURSELF

1030
00:56:34,725 --> 00:56:37,893
IN A VERY DIFFERENT WAY,
AND I RESPECT THAT.

1031
00:56:37,895 --> 00:56:39,928
I'M JUST WONDERING

1032
00:56:39,930 --> 00:56:42,898
